11. What is the output of this code snippet?
int x = 5;
x += 3;
System.out.println(x);

12. Identify the error in the following code:
int num = "10";
System.out.println(num);

13. What is wrong with this code?
double val = 10;
int num = val;

14. What will this output?
int a = 7;
int b = 2;
System.out.println(a / b);

15. Which line will cause a compilation error?
int x = 5;
x = x + 2.5;

16. What is the output?
int x = 10;
x -= 4;
System.out.println(x);

17. What does the following code print?
int x = 3;
int y = 4;
System.out.println(x * y + 2);

19. What is wrong with this snippet?
Scanner input = new Scanner(System.in);
System.out.println("Enter a number:");
int num = input.nextLine();

20. What is the output?
int result = 5;
result *= 2 + 3;
System.out.println(result);
